data.description: Lower price than builder & SELLER OFFERING $10K CREDIT TO BUYER. This newly built 2021 home is located in the new community of Verona. The home backs up to community conservation with oversized lot offering more additional yard space than what is currently offered in the new construction phases. Upgraded front elevation. Upgraded tile flooring. Kitchen has upgraded cabinets, large island, & upgraded GRANITE countertops. Owner added upgraded Stainless Steal Refrigerator and large stainless steel single basin sink. Primary bedroom boasts a large walk in closet, bathroom with dual sink vanity and additional closet. Dedicated laundry room with shelving.  Yard is fully fenced w/ a large covered patio. Future amenities already under construction: Clubhouse, Resort Style Pool, Splash Pad, Fitness Center, and Tot Lot. Sidewalks throughout neighborhood. Close to KSC, Port Canaveral and local beaches!
